ngo At Home","display_priority":35}],"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/1017163-4/watch?locale=US","rent":[{"logo_path":"/qR6FKvnPBx2O37FDg8PNM7efwF3.jpg","provider_id":10,"provider_name":"Amazon Video","display_priority":6},{"logo_path":"/SPnB1qiCkYfirS2it3hZORwGVn.jpg","provider_id":2,"provider_name":"Apple TV Store","display_priority":7},{"logo_path":"/8z7rC8uIDaTM91X0ZfkRf04ydj2.jpg","provider_id":3,"provider_name":"Google Play Movies","display_priority":16},{"logo_path":"/pTnn5JwWr4p3pG8H6VrpiQo7Vs0.jpg","provider_id":192,"provider_name":"YouTube","display_priority":17},{"logo_path":"/19fkcOz0xeUgCVW8tO85uOYnYK9.jpg","provider_id":7,"provider_name":"Fandango At Home","display_priority":35}],"flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/bxBlRPEPpMVDc4jMhSrTf2339DW.jpg","provider_id":15,"provider_name":"Hulu","display_priority":8}]}}},"wikidata_id":"Q115283311","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-07T14:49:53.785279+00:00","region":"KR","main_poster":null,"images":null,"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:12:41.59+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"거침없이 싹 쓸어버린다","homepage":"","overview":"신종 마약 사건 3년 뒤, 괴물형사 마석도와 서울 광수대는 배달앱을 이용한 마약 판매 사건을 수사하던 중 수배 중인 앱 개발자가 필리핀에서 사망한 사건이 대규모 온라인 불법 도박 조직과 연관되어 있음을 알아낸다. 필리핀에 거점을 두고 납치, 감금, 폭행, 살인 등으로 대한민국 온라인 불법 도박 시장을 장악한 특수부대 용병 출신의 빌런 백창기와 한국에서 더 큰 판을 짜고 있는 IT업계 천재 CEO 장동철. 마석도는 더 커진 판을 잡기 위해 장이수에게 뜻밖의 협력을 제안하고 광역수사대는 물론, 사이버수사대까지 합류해 범죄를 소탕하기 시작하는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"The Roundup: Punishment","runtime":109,"tagline":"Time for the ultimate wipeout.","homepage":"","overview":"'Monster Cop' Ma Seok-do investigates an illegal online gambling business led by a former STS Baek and an IT genius CEO Chang. Ma proposes an unexpected alliance to Jang and begins hunting down the criminals."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"The Roundup: Punishment","runtime":109,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Während der Ermittlungen gegen die Betreiber einer App für Drogenhandel stoßen Detective Ma (Don Lee) und sein Team auf eine Verbindung zwischen einem Mordfall auf den Philippinen und einer illegalen Organisation für Onlineglücksspiel. Deren Anführer, IT-Genie Chang Dong-cheol, und sein Komplize, Ex-Elitesoldat Baek Chang-gi, stecken bereits in den Vorbereitungen für ihren nächsten großen Schachzug. Um ihre Pläne zu vereiteln, weitet Detective Ma die Operation aus und schmiedet dafür eine ungewöhnliche Allianz ..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪都市4","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「怪物刑警」马锡道（马东锡 饰）这次要对抗的是规模最大的网络非法赌博组织首脑．白昌其（金武烈 饰），他是特种部队佣兵出身的恶徒；另外还要对付IT业界出身的天才CEO．张东哲（李东辉 饰）。马锡道将与华丽回归的张夷秀（朴智焕 饰）、广搜队及网络搜查队合作，展开更胜以往的扫荡行动！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪都市４","runtime":109,"tagline":"我會負責將他們一網打盡","homepage":"","overview":"在解決新興毒品案件後的三年後，「怪物刑警」馬錫道與首爾廣搜隊在搜查利用外送APP販毒的案件時，發現遭通緝的APP開發者在菲律賓死亡的案件與大規模的網路非法賭博組織有關。特種部隊傭兵出身的白昌其，在菲律賓設置據點，以綁架、監禁、暴力及殺人等手段，掌控韓國網路非法賭博市場；IT業界出身的天才CEO，張東哲則在韓國籌備規模更大的計畫。馬錫道為了將壞傢伙們一網打盡，決定與張夷帥、廣搜隊及網路搜查隊合作，展開更勝以往的掃蕩行動！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Криминальный город 4","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Детектив Ма Сок-то создал отдел по борьбе с киберпреступлениями и пытается поймать организаторов крупнейшего в стране нелегального онлайн-казино."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"บู๊ระห่ำล่าล้างนรก: นรกลงทัณฑ์","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"สามปีหลังจากเหตุการณ์กวาดล้างแก๊งยาเสพติดในเกาหลี สุดยอดตำรวจมือปราบอย่าง มาซอกโด(ดอน ลี) และหน่วยสืบสวนนครบาลก็ยุ่งอยู่กับการไล่ล่าอาชญากรที่ค้ายาเสพติดผ่านทางแอพเดลิเวอรี่ จนมาพบว่าผู้เผยแพร่แอพนี้ได้เสียชีวิตอยู่ที่ฟิลิปปินส์ ไม่นานนักพวกเขาก็เชื่อมโยงได้ว่าคดีนี้น่าจะเกี่ยวพันกับธุรกิจพนันออนไลน์ผิดกฎหมายที่ใหญ่โตซึ่งมีความเชื่อมโยงกันอย่างผิดปกติ ในฟิลิปปินส์อดีตนักรบรับจ้างกองกำลังพิเศษอย่าง แบกชางกี(คิมมูยอล) ก็ได้รวบอำนาจเบ็ดเสร็จในวงการพนันออนไลน์ผิดกฎหมายของเกาหลีด้วยวิธีการลักพาตัว กักขัง และทำร้ายร่างกายหรือแม้กระทั่งฆาตกรรม ขณะเดียวกันในเกาหลีซีอีโออัจฉริยะด้านไอที ชางดงชอล(อีดงฮวี) ก็กำลังวางแผนการที่ยิ่งใหญ่กว่านั้น นักสืบมาซอกโด ได้ขอความช่วยเหลือจาก จางอีซู (พัคจีฮวาน) และด้วยความสนับสนุนจากทีมสืบสวนไซเบอร์ หน่วยสืบสวนนครบาลก็เริ่มรวบตัวอาชญากรบางคน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪都市：鐵拳清算","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「怪物刑警」馬石道（馬東石 飾）聯同網路調查組，狙擊韓國最大非法網絡賭博組織。掃蕩過程中，「怪物刑警」既要迎戰特種部隊出身的冷血首領白昌基（金武烈 飾），又要智取幕後主腦虛擬幣業界的 CEO 兼 IT 天才張東哲（李東輝 飾），鐵拳升級越戰越勇，清算賭網罪犯只求有揼錯，無放過！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Büntetlenül 4","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Egy kábítószer-kereskedelemmel foglalkozó alkalmazás után való nyomozás közben, Ma Suk Do és csapata kapcsolatot talál, az alkalmazás Fülöp-szigeteken meggyilkolt fejlesztője és egy illegális online szerencsejáték-szervezet között.\r Eközben a Fülöp-szigeteken Baek Chang Ki irányítja a koreai illegális online szerencsejáték-piacot, s emberrablással és gyilkossággal tartja magánál a hatalmat. Társa, az IT-zseni Jang Dong Cheol egy még nagyobb tervet eszel ki Koreában.\r Azért, hogy véget vessen a fokozódó fenyegetésnek, Ma nyomozónak váratlan szövetséget kell kötnie …"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Қылмысқа толы қала 4","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Қылмысқа толы қала 4"},"name":"қазақ","iso_639_1":"kk","iso_3166_1":"KZ","english_name":"Kazakh"},{"data":{"title":"Vây Hãm 4: Kẻ Trừng Phạt","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"'Monster Cop' Ma Seok-do điều tra một doanh nghiệp cờ bạc trực tuyến bất hợp pháp do cựu STS Baek và CEO thiên tài CNTT Chang đứng đầu. Ma đề xuất một liên minh bất ngờ với Jang và bắt đầu truy lùng tội phạm."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Fuerza bruta: Castigo","runtime":109,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mientras investigan una aplicación de tráfico de drogas, Ma Seok-do y su equipo descubren una conexión entre el desarrollador de la aplicación, asesinado en Filipinas, y una organización de apuestas ilegales online. Mientras tanto, en Filipinas, Baek Chang-gi controla el mercado coreano de apuestas ilegales y siembra el terror con secuestros, agresiones y asesinatos. Su socio, el genio informático Chang Dong-cheol, planea un plan aún mayor en la propia Corea. Para poner fin a la creciente amenaza, el detective Ma amplía su operación proponiendo una alianza inesperada... Cuarta entrega de la exitosa franquicia de acción surcoreana 'The Roundup'."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"'Monster Cop' Ma Seok-do onderzoekt een illegaal online gokbedrijf onder leiding van een voormalige STS Baek en een IT-genie CEO Chang. Ma stelt Jang een onverwachte alliantie voor en begint de jacht op de criminelen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Psanci: Konečná pomsta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Detektiv Ma Sok-to zřídil jednotku pro boj s kyberkriminalitou a snaží se dopadnout organizátory největšího nelegálního online kasina v zemi."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"The Roundup: Punishment","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Le détective Ma Seok Do travaille sur une affaire de trafique de drogue impliquant l'utilisation d'une application de livraison.  Baek Chang Ki est le nouveau criminel que Ma Seok Do doit arrêter mais celui-ci se trouve aux Philippines et pour couronner le tout, ce dernier a un complice qui est à Séoul."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Кримінальне місто 4","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Детектив Ма Сок-то створив відділ боротьби з кіберзлочинами і намагається зловити організаторів найбільшого в країні нелегального онлайн-казино."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"'Monster Cop' Ma Seok-do investighează o afacere ilegală de jocuri de noroc online condusă de un fost STS Baek și un CEO al geniului IT Chang. Ma îi propune lui Jang o alianță neașteptată și începe să-i vâneze pe criminali."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"قانون شکنان 4 : مجازات","runtime":109,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"درباره کارآگاه ما سوک-دو و تیم اوست که در حال بررسی یک اپلیکیشن قاچاق مواد مخدر هستند. آن‌ها متوجه ارتباط این اپلیکیشن با یک سازمان بزرگ قمار آنلاین غیرقانونی می‌شوند. این تحقیقات آن‌ها را به فیلیپین می‌برد، جایی که بک چانگ-گی، سرباز سابق نخبه، با کنترل بازار قمار آنلاین کره، با اقدامات خشونت‌آمیز خود مثل آدم‌ربایی، حمله و قتل ترس و وحشت ایجاد کرده است. به منظور پایان دادن به این تهدید فزاینده، ما سوک-دو تصمیم می‌گیرد که عملیات خود را با همکاری واحد سایبری و تیم تحقیقات مترو گسترش دهد و بزرگترین ماموریت خود را برای شکار مجرمان آغاز کند"},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"الإغارة: العقاب الخارجون عن القانون 4","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور الاحداث حول محقق الجرائم العنيف ما سوك-دو يتولى التحقيق في نشاط مقامرة غير قانوني عبر الإنترنت يديره بايك، عضو سابق في STS، ورئيس تنفيذي بارع في تكنولوجيا المعلومات يُدعى تشانغ. يقترح ما شراكة مفاجئة مع جانغ ويبدأ في تعقب المجرمين."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Престъпен град 4: Наказание","runtime":109,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Докато разследват приложение за трафик на наркотици, детектив Ма Сок До и неговият екип откриват връзка между разработчика на приложението, който е убит във Филипините, и нелегална организация за онлайн хазарт. Междувременно във Филипините Пек Чанг Ги контролира корейския пазар на нелегален онлайн хазарт, включително чрез отвличания, нападения и убийства. Неговият партньор, ИТ геният Чанг Донг Чол, планира още по-голяма схема в Корея. За да сложи край на ескалиращата заплаха, детектив Ма разширява операцията си, като предлага неочакван съюз..."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪都市 PUNISHMENT","runtime":0,"tagline":"拳 VS IT犯罪","homepage":"","overview":"マ・ドンソクがタフガイ刑事マ・ソクトを演じる人気ポリスアクション「犯罪都市」シリーズの第4作。マ・ソクトとそのチームは、韓国とフィリピンを股にかけた組織と対決！ 監督はシリーズ第1～3作でアクション監督を務めたホ・ミョンヘン。\r 新種合成麻薬事件から 3 年後。ヤクザも恐れる怪物刑事マ・ソクト（マ・ドンソク）とソウル広域捜査隊は、デリバリーアプリを悪用した麻薬密売事件を捜査していた。捜査を進めるうち、手配中のアプリ開発者が謎の死を遂げた事件の背後に、フィリピンに拠点を置く国際 IT 犯罪組織の存在を突き止める。組織のリーダーは、拉致、監禁、暴行、殺人をいとわず、韓国の違法オンラインカジノ市場を掌握した、特殊部隊出身の“元傭兵”ペク・チャンギ（キム・ムヨル）。一方、組織オーナーで“IT の天才”CEO チャン・ドンチョル（イ・ドンフィ）は、韓国でさらに大きな犯罪計画を練っていた。マ刑事は、史上最大規模の IT 犯罪計画を殲滅するため、オンラインカジノ事業の経験を持つチャン・イス（パク・ジファン）に捜査協力を依頼し、広域捜査隊、サイバー捜査隊と新たなチームを結成し捜査を始めるのだが……。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Suçu kökten kurutmak için geri dönüyor.","homepage":"","overview":"Güney Kore yapımı bir aksiyon filmi olup ve \"The Roundup\" serisinin devamı niteliğindedir. Film, dedektif Ma Seok-do'nun (Don Lee) heyecan dolu maceralarını sürdürüyor ve onu yeni bir suç çetesiyle karşı karşıya getiriyor. Ma Seok-do, uluslararası bir suç örgütünün peşine düşmektedir. Bu suç örgütü, insan kaçakçılığı ve uyuşturucu ticareti gibi yasadışı faaliyetlerle uğraşmaktadır. Dedektifimiz, bu tehlikeli çetenin lideri olan acımasız bir suçlu ile yüzleşmek zorunda kalır. Ancak, Ma Seok-do'nun karşısındaki düşman sadece fiziksel güç değil; aynı zamanda zekâ ve strateji gerektiren bir rakiptir. Ma Seok-do, geçmişte yaşadığı kayıplar ve içsel çatışmalarla yüzleşirken, izleyicilere onun kararlılığını ve adalet arayışını gösteriyor. Ayrıca, filmdeki yan karakterler de oldukça önemli bir rol oynuyor; bazıları dostken, bazıları da haindir. Adaletin peşinde koşan bir adamın hikâyesini anlatırken, aynı zamanda insan doğasının karanlık yönlerine de ışık tutuyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Bezkarni - ostateczna odpłata","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"Monster Cop\" Ma Seok-do bada nielegalny biznes hazardowy online prowadzony przez byłego STS Baek i geniusza IT CEO Chang. Ma proponuje Jangowi nieoczekiwany sojusz i rozpoczyna polowanie na przestępców."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Força Bruta: Punição","runtime":109,"tagline":"Hora do Acerto Final.","homepage":"","overview":"O detetive Ma Seok-do se junta à Equipe de Investigação Cibernética para capturar um ex-mercenário e líder de uma organização de apostas online. Juntos, eles enfrentam o crime digital em uma operação de alto risco."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Psanci 4: Konečná pomsta","runtime":0,"tagline":"Čas na definitívne zničenie.","homepage":"","overview":"Pri vyšetrovaní aplikácie pre obchod s drogami objaví detektív Seok-do Ma (Dong-seok Ma) a jeho tím spojenie medzi vývojárom aplikácie, ktorý bol zavraždený na Filipínach, a nelegálnym online hazardným krúžkom. Detektív sa pripojí ku kybernetickému vyšetrovaciemu tímu, aby tak dopadol Baeka Chang-kiho, bývalého žoldniera a šéfa organizácie zaoberajúcej sa online hazardom."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"The Roundup: Punishment","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nelle Filippine un giovane programmatore coreano viene trovato morto dopo una lunga prigionia. Le indagini svelano un racket di casinò online tra Corea e Filippine, gestito dal criminale Baek Chang-gi e legato al magnate IT Chang Dong-cheol. L'agente Ma Seok-do promette giustizia. Riuscirà a smantellare la rete criminale?"},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mentre investiguen una aplicació de tràfic de drogues, en Ma Seok-do i el seu equip descobreixen una connexió entre el desenvolupador de l'aplicació, assassinat a les Filipines, i una organització d'apostes il·legals en línia. Mentrestant, a les Filipines, en Baek Chang-gi controla el mercat coreà d'apostes il·legals i sembra el terror amb segrestos, agressions i assassinats. El seu soci, el geni informàtic Chang Dong-cheol, planeja un pla encara més gran a la mateixa Corea. Per posar fi a la creixent amenaça, el detectiu Ma amplia la seva operació proposant una aliança inesperada..."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"The Roundup 4: Punishment","runtime":109,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"När kriminalpolisen tillika muskelpaketet Ma utreder en app för droghandel uppdagas en koppling mellan appens utvecklare, som hittats mördad i Filippinerna och ett globalt, brottsligt nätverk. Om Ma ska kunna stoppa den internationella konspirationen måste han bilda en oväntad allians…"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"668715420da304d635d08ce1","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/668715420da304d635d08ce1","author":"MovieGuys","content":"I really enjoy The Roundup franchise, its fast , paced, simple fun. That said, I'm not quite so enthusiastic about the latest film Punishment.\r\n\r\nWhat makes these films work is simple fast paced, frenetic action combined with top class choreography. This film certainly has most of these elements but it doesn't work as well. Why? \r\n\r\nPerhaps its biggest short coming is its not especially cohesive. It builds and diffuses its much needed pace.This is not helped at all by  jumping between geographical locations and complicating the team dynamic. \r\n\r\nThe main character behaving like a medieval vassal, getting on his knees at one point to beg to keep a case, didn't impress either. Nor does, the at times, rather lame humour,that feels tacked on.\r\n\r\nOn the upside what remains is moderately entertaining but its not enough to really see this iteration shine.\r\n\r\nIn summary, not every film in any franchise can be a winner. The Roundup: Punishment is not awful but its not all that good either.","created_at":"2024-07-04T21:33:54.338Z","updated_at":"2024-07-04T21:34:41.133Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1075754,"adult":false,"title":"Second Act","video":false,"overview":"The great star of the Royal Dramatic Theatre has fallen ill, and must be cared for at home by a talkative, insecure woman who, over time, finds it difficult to maintain the professional boundaries of the relationship.","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2851,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/ujsFVgMVXzrV5TkChEWAm5iLjk4.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-24","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/pa4wy20Hr0JQcTKnMy3hDesL0Ap.jpg","original_title":"Andra akten","original_language":"sv"},{"id":172744,"adult":false,"title":"Burning Sensation","video":false,"overview":"A firefighter salvages a spiritual shrine from an old burning building, which releases the gentle ghost of a Chinese opera singer, killed in a stage fire 30 years before. Grateful for saving her, the ghost falls for the firefighter and will stop at nothing to ensure his safety from the evils that lurk ahead. At the same time, the firefighter doesn't realize he is dating a ghost.","genre_ids":[35,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0194,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/rS8xwIubARql8DnXGmvoA9fbpqk.jpg","release_date":"1989-05-06","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/509LcKpgM0aSDFeGUvWedl5xpqQ.jpg","original_title":"火燭鬼","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1275176,"adult":false,"title":"Arnold & Sly: Rivals, Friends, Icons","video":false,"overview":"TMZ exclusively sits down with Arnold Schwarzenegger and Sylvester Stallone as they discuss for the first time how their once-fierce rivalry led to two Hollywood icons forever being friends and brothers in arms.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3399,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/8LGiYX7vR0Tnk7YNJ7Wx8C1VVX9.jpg","release_date":"2024-04-23","vote_average":9.3,"backdrop_path":"/3LIM0ynznzag0RNI6nHgYQH1brM.jpg","original_title":"Arnold & Sly: Rivals, Friends, Icons","original_language":"en"},{"id":514743,"adult":false,"title":"Cordelia","video":false,"overview":"Cordelia ia a troubled, damaged soul who is only just recovering after some unnamed trauma; she is an actor rehearsing a play and comes to stay in a creepy London mansion flat occupied by her twin sister Caroline and Caroline’s boyfriend Matt. When they leave her alone there  Cordelia strikes up a friendship with Frank the charming, but strange and unreliable young man they can hear practising his cello in the upstairs flat – a relationship which quickly becomes very disturbing.","genre_ids":[18,53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9142,"vote_count":42,"poster_path":"/3LD2EaAxV09Md3RK5gIYx0RQw7X.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-25","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/4NwPaKEUchvPXCqAOyUvkTjrEfA.jpg","original_title":"Cordelia","original_language":"en"},{"id":950075,"adult":false,"title":"Sookshmadarshini","video":false,"overview":"Manuel returns with his mother to their former home in a middle-class neighbourhood. Suspicious of his intentions, Priyadarshini and her friends begin gathering clues, convinced he may be hiding something sinister.","genre_ids":[9648,53,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8564,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/rOZt5FVZC51keFRRUSzWGE5y1Rt.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-22","vote_average":7.446,"backdrop_path":"/jdSLtUpElZuKkqlY85n6YHZhVWB.jpg","original_title":"സൂക്ഷ്മദര്‍ശിനി","original_language":"ml"},{"id":55847,"adult":false,"title":"Four Nights of a Dreamer","video":false,"overview":"Jacques, a young man with artistic aspirations, spends four nights wandering Paris with a young woman, whom he rescued from suicide.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5673,"vote_count":106,"poster_path":"/cVzvJsn2TUEXxRszs2IVFF36hSA.jpg","release_date":"1972-02-02","vote_average":7.108,"backdrop_path":"/5kh4VMRflkmlOcvnB0WW2LgbZg9.jpg","original_title":"Quatre nuits d'un rêveur","original_language":"fr"},{"id":348689,"adult":false,"title":"Memories of the Sword","video":false,"overview":"While in medieval Korea, a young girl sets out to revenge the betrayal and the death of her mother. But therefore she must face one of the most powerful men and warriors of the Goryeo Dynasty.","genre_ids":[18,36,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6202,"vote_count":105,"poster_path":"/dqf7fnJXoPvKdVD33w4KYl3qB55.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-13","vote_average":6.605,"backdrop_path":"/e50DTFe9hOgCEDfinYkAhZojoU.jpg","original_title":"협녀, 칼의 기억","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1442776,"adult":false,"title":"Crazy Lizard","video":false,"overview":"A young man climbs into the mountains to pick up a meteorite that has fallen there and is killed by something. The \"thing\" descends to the village and begins to eat the inhabitants one by one, terrorizing the entire island.","genre_ids":[28,53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1264,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/9TFaFsSXedaALXTzba349euDeoY.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-27","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/zxjFabSJKMAvuu3acNg78nuTuCs.jpg","original_title":"狂暴巨蜥","original_language":"zh"},{"id":805455,"adult":false,"title":"White Snake: Love Tribulation","video":false,"overview":"The two sisters of Lingshe Mountain - White Snake and Green Snake - devoted themselves to cultivating of immortality. The White Snake was in danger during the tribulation. Fortunately, Xu Xian, who went to the mountain to search for medicine, rescued her. In a dream White Snake learns the words of the poem \"Enter the world, know the warmth and the cold\" and enters the city in search of a cause. The Great Demon King of the Yin Division coveted the White Snake's pearl for nearly a thousand years. Knowing that the White Snake is alive, he sent his subordinate judges to seal the city for her search. White Snake meets Xu Xian and cures his classmate Gao Jin's critically ill father. When he finds out that the White Snake is a demon, he tells the Underworld that he will take revenge.","genre_ids":[10749,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6282,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/6EAiZJk4ErjDpypl3p5aB5oRDB9.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-12","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/cYtf9LXty9xMWrLOC1wCrcfpGdM.jpg","original_title":"白蛇：情劫","original_language":"zh"},{"id":171587,"adult":false,"title":"Whatcha Wearin'?","video":false,"overview":"Yoon-jung accidentally calls a stranger, instead of her boyfriend, and has phone sex with the unknown man. When Yoon-jung's relationship with her boyfriend turns sour, Yoon-jung meets Hyun-seung, the stranger she had phone sex with.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.4029,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/acoytVakE7E8lCSB4JM7KyV9Ft9.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-06","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/gcitkvOxToHSTBHvrhBFrqMTKBt.jpg","original_title":"나의 PS 파트너","original_language":"ko"},{"id":12237,"adult":false,"title":"Faces of Death","video":false,"overview":"A collection of death scenes, ranging from TV-material to home-made super-8 movies. The common factor is death by some means.","genre_ids":[27,99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5832,"vote_count":197,"poster_path":"/fhHzqDrdHLqjawXLXoV3w4FDOUd.jpg","release_date":"1978-11-10","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/f81NvyLKg23gv5Rw3o7uHmupyte.jpg","original_title":"Faces of Death","original_language":"en"},{"id":888001,"adult":false,"title":"River of Fear","video":false,"overview":"A local guide is asked to lead a group of influencers along the river of a remote valley. As they get deeper into the wilderness, their venture takes a frightening turn.","genre_ids":[53,9648,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9123,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/8Q0sJtvbhkPJ1jXzvYW7qzgcupk.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-21","vote_average":5.585,"backdrop_path":"/mpxTLzAs7Os3SnjtnjqZ6PzOgae.jpg","original_title":"Upurga","original_language":"lv"},{"id":1250620,"adult":false,"title":"La coda del diavolo","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3288,"vote_count":53,"poster_path":"/lc59jGDtB8KVnsZk76C7RwZnWkJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-25","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/6xOQkM621sqORs19n581ifw0Ek4.jpg","original_title":"La coda del diavolo","original_language":"it"},{"id":197158,"adult":false,"title":"Porno!","video":false,"overview":"Three tales of the erotic: Two young ladies experiment with lesbianism, a handsome and wealthy socialite makes a beautiful woman patiently wait to make love to him, and a gorgeous, but controlling and dominating blind woman makes a hunky stud her sexual hostage in her swanky mansion home.","genre_ids":[18,27,14,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8693,"vote_count":84,"poster_path":"/bhbPSpYjsRJAK7rXqL8APK9EwBl.jpg","release_date":"1981-01-01","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/8eAVBvK7ux51Ab9edZLbvCjEbbt.jpg","original_title":"Pornô!","original_language":"pt"},{"id":1299537,"adult":false,"title":"Successor","video":false,"overview":"Ma Chenggang, a wealthy man in Xihong City, worries that his eldest son is too spoiled to succeed him. Determined to raise a capable successor, he takes an unconventional approach. They conceal their wealth, moving the family to a dilapidated neighborhood, and maintain an illusion of poverty, so that his son could develop qualities such as hard work, knowledge, careful budgeting, physical fitness, and perseverance.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.815,"vote_count":82,"poster_path":"/jqGZEk4sLGGmIXBDQzxTuT1lZx2.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-13","vote_average":6.97,"backdrop_path":"/9ir1UZYWBZBkgCoRUIV0ffk43Xe.jpg","original_title":"抓娃娃","original_language":"zh"},{"id":4723,"adult":false,"title":"Southland Tales","video":false,"overview":"Set in the futuristic landscape of Los Angeles on July 4, 2008, as it stands on the brink of social, economic and environmental disaster. Boxer Santaros is an action star who's stricken with amnesia. His life intertwines with Krysta Now, an adult film star developing her own reality television project, and Ronald Taverner, a Hermosa Beach police officer who holds the key to a vast conspiracy.","genre_ids":[878,53,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6544,"vote_count":591,"poster_path":"/7dbIDQ80z4bxiDlAvxRwc5TI44C.jpg","release_date":"2007-11-14","vote_average":5.217,"backdrop_path":"/oaT5yMG61XetddVmymGrDVeoCg4.jpg","original_title":"Southland Tales","original_language":"en"},{"id":479718,"adult":false,"title":"The Outlaws","video":false,"overview":"In Chinatown, law and order is turned upside down when a trio of feral Chinese gangsters arrive, start terrorizing civilians, and usurping territory. The beleaguered local gangsters team up with the police, lead by the badass loose cannon Ma Seok-do, to bring them down. Based on a true story.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.0422,"vote_count":513,"poster_path":"/khJo0VTt1uDHOqgI4igXHNPj2LW.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-03","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/xord8lZ7mK8ctki6FBgNYrbpWCO.jpg","original_title":"범죄도시","original_language":"ko"},{"id":376424,"adult":false,"title":"Beware the Slenderman","video":false,"overview":"In this horrifyingly modern fairytale lurks an online Boogeyman and two 12-year-old girls who would kill for him. The entrance to the internet quickly leads to its darkest basement. How responsible are our children for what they find there?","genre_ids":[99,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3698,"vote_count":263,"poster_path":"/f5W2nhbnzOR2aNa7vSpwWCzzAw2.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-11","vote_average":6.496,"backdrop_path":"/eRT7t3W7iAqaDDWaJq8wnkIAuk4.jpg","original_title":"Beware the Slenderman","original_language":"en"},{"id":591120,"adult":false,"title":"The Pirates: The Last Royal Treasure","video":false,"overview":"A gutsy crew of Joseon pirates and bandits battle stormy waters, puzzling clues and militant rivals in search of royal gold lost at sea.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6145,"vote_count":223,"poster_path":"/50UQeTrUM7ErXzkvqCsV6EXcM3g.jpg","release_date":"2022-01-26","vote_average":6.504,"backdrop_path":"/pwpw1veVNW2Sls5sGbA9mqMYN49.jpg","original_title":"해적: 도깨비 깃발","original_language":"ko"}],"similar_content":[{"id":5236,"adult":false,"title":"Kiss Kiss Bang Bang","video":false,"overview":"A petty thief posing as an actor is brought to Los Angeles for an unlikely audition and finds himself in the middle of a murder investigation along with his high school dream girl and a detective who's been training him for his upcoming role...","genre_ids":[35,80,9648,53],"popularity":2.5977,"vote_count":2935,"poster_path":"/aWfjIkpENFX6Uw82pET7EQ6jnrd.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-14","vote_average":7.158,"backdrop_path":"/x29PYzoNYPGzdj3M8FDwSwEgNpf.jpg","original_title":"Kiss Kiss Bang Bang","original_language":"en"},{"id":5289,"adult":false,"title":"Chaos","video":false,"overview":"In Seattle, detective Quentin Conners is unfairly suspended and his partner Jason York leaves the police force after a tragic shooting on Pearl Street Bridge, when the hostage and the criminal die. During a bank heist with a hostage situation, Conners is assigned in charge of the operation with the rookie Shane Dekker as his partner. The thieves, lead by Lorenz, apparently do not steal a penny from the bank. While chasing the gangsters, the police team disclose that they planted a virus in the system, stealing one billion dollars from the different accounts, using the principle of the Chaos Theory. Further, they find that Lorenz is killing his accomplices.","genre_ids":[18,28,80],"popularity":6.6104,"vote_count":1120,"poster_path":"/fsqOoouBsNo69vbh2WG6PtpzGBa.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-17","vote_average":6.318,"backdrop_path":"/7hw6P8Xq8pNcIcuTknDIn5qcm3Y.jpg","original_title":"Chaos","original_language":"en"},{"id":5677,"adult":false,"title":"Trancers","video":false,"overview":"Angel City trooper Jack Deth is sent back in time from 2247 to 1985 L.A. to inhabit the body of his ancestor. Deth's assignment is to find his archenemy, Whistler, who turns people into zombies, before the fiend is able to kill all the ancestors of the future's governing council.","genre_ids":[878,80],"popularity":2.7145,"vote_count":221,"poster_path":"/4Qx4KrimPXFNw8yRUBaZldcN8Ma.jpg","release_date":"1984-11-07","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/ubl78MVPqDBWkWPl16lzkgSwiQb.jpg","original_title":"Trancers","original_language":"en"},{"id":467306,"adult":false,"title":"Playing with Dolls: Havoc","video":false,"overview":"When serial killer Havoc escapes from his prison, there is no holding back. He descends upon unsuspecting lovers in their cabin get away. The world's most brutal killer is loose and his thirst for blood cannot be stopped.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":0.7056,"v